          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p> Directs the Secretary of the Army to establish a chain of command for Army national military cemeteries, including a military commander of the Army National Military Cemeteries to replace the current civilian director upon the termination of the tenure of such director.</p>]]></text>
